@startuml

actor Instructor
actor Student
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "File Storage\nService" as FileStorage
participant "Email & Notification\nService" as Notification

' Login & Navigation Flow
Instructor -> Frontend: Log In to LMS
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Authenticate User
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Login Successful
deactivate Backend
Instructor -> Frontend: Navigate to Grading Panel
Frontend -> Backend: Request Assignment List
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Assignments
deactivate Backend
Instructor -> Frontend: Select Assignment to Grade
Frontend -> Backend: Load Submission List
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Ungraded Submissions
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend

' Grading Flow
Instructor -> Frontend: Open Student Submission
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Request Submission Content
activate Backend
Backend -> FileStorage: Retrieve Submission File
activate FileStorage
FileStorage --> Backend: Submission File Content
deactivate FileStorage
Backend --> Frontend: Display Submission
deactivate Backend
Instructor -> Frontend: Enter Grade, Write Feedback & Attach Rubric
Frontend -> Backend: Submit Grade & Feedback
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Grade Validated & Saved
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend

' Statistics Flow
Backend -> Backend: Compute Assignment Statistics & Update Grade Report

' Student Notification Flow
Backend -> Notification: Send Feedback Notification to Student
activate Notification
Notification --> Student: Receive Feedback Notification
deactivate Notification
Student -> Frontend: Log In & View Grade & Feedback
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Request Grade & Feedback
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Grade & Feedback
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend

' Grade Dispute Flow
Student -> Frontend: Submit Regrade Request with Reason
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Submit Regrade Request
activate Backend
Backend --> Instructor: Regrade Request Forwarded
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend
Instructor -> Frontend: Review & Respond to Regrade Request
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Submit Regrade Decision
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Grade Updated or Denied
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend
Backend -> Notification: Notify Student of Regrade Decision
activate Notification
Notification --> Student: Receive Regrade Decision
deactivate Notification

@enduml
